<html>
 <head>
  <title>The org.infogrid.util.text package</title>
 </head>
 <body>
  <p>Classes similar to the ones found in package <code>java.text</code> but more flexible.</p>
  <p>Most importantly, this package defines the notion of a
     {@link org.infogrid.util.text.Stringifier Stringifier}, which allows both the
     generation and parsing of arbitrary <code>Objects</code> (and groups of
     <code>Objects</code>) to and from text. It is essentially a more powerful
     replacement for <code>java.text.MessageFormat</code>.</p>
 </body>
</html>
